 聞兩聞就跑走<br />\n日日坐係個竇到發呆, 又唔太玩唔太跑<br />\n我驚佢有抑鬱...有咩方法可以令佢快啲適應?</blockquote><br />\n小露寶係咁 希望你唔好棄養都唔好搵多隻陪佢 打交打到死<br />\n由佢自己習慣下先<br />\n大幾兩三個星期就試下請佢食零食 <br />\n睇下佢會唔會接啦</blockquote><br />\n係咪呢世都唔會上到手</blockquote><br />\n我養緊呢隻好神經質又惡都上到手 俾少少耐性啦"},{"pid":"382c10e3690559bffa5575825338822bc17dd7cd","tid":225123,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T22:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/062413_6bfdd4285664896600cf85c7798e0368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F062413_6bfdd4285664896600cf85c7798e0368.jpg&h=9ff05dce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/062446_12f676b03d5dca3a497833d7ea49ad7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F062446_12f676b03d5dca3a497833d7ea49ad7a.jpg&h=b4b44321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝巴打早日成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23499f8f4b7bef3fa8e90393b71d3bf349974caa","tid":225123,"uid":28015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/062413_6bfdd4285664896600cf85c7798e0368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F062413_6bfdd4285664896600cf85c7798e0368.jpg&h=9ff05dce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/062446_12f676b03d5dca3a497833d7ea49ad7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F062446_12f676b03d5dca3a497833d7ea49ad7a.jpg&h=b4b44321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝巴打早日成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢而家最多都係咬下我隻手<br />\nBtw你拎佢出籠怕唔怕佢跑走"},{"pid":"5133deee23b920c6c5ab1fb80d0ebe16bb49ca68","tid":225123,"uid":517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/062413_6bfdd4285664896600cf85c7798e0368.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F062413_6bfdd4285664896600cf85c7798e0368.jpg&h=9ff05dce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/06/062446_12f676b03d5dca3a497833d7ea49ad7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F06%2F062446_12f676b03d5dca3a497833d7ea49ad7a.jpg&h=b4b44321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝巴打早日成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢而家最多都係咬下我隻手<br />\nBtw你拎佢出籠怕唔怕佢跑走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上左手 佢就唔會走佬/跳樓<br />\n最多好似第一張咁發呆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49433a17adc8615189b77219041878b03df9c382","tid":225123,"uid":85150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"倉鼠之中最鍾意小露寶，細細隻個樣又得意<br />\n上手唔難不過唔會定，成日極速由手爬到去背再上頭頭"}]}